Game : Virtua Tennis 2 Sega Professional tennis * 50/60Hz * (c) Sega Sports
Release.....: November 24th, 2001
Origin......: EURO/PAL
Ripped.......: Nothing

- Choose from 16 internationally ranked men's and women's tennis players including:
Venus Williams, Serena Williams, Monica Seles, Lindsay Davenport, 
Magnus Norman,Patrick Rafter, Yevgeny Kafelnikov, Mary Pierce, Jelena Dokic
Arantxa Sanchez-Vicario,Alexandra Stevenson, Carlos Moya, Tim Henman, 
Cedric Pioline, Tommy Haas and Thomas Enqvist.

-Complete in singles, doubles, & the all-new mixed doubles matches with up 
to four players.

-Newly revamped modes of play -- Arcade Mode, Exhibition Mode, 
and World Circuit Mode.

-Create, train, and enter your player in tournament where you'll compete 
against top-ranked opponents around the world for the #1 world ranking.

-Stunningly realistic camera angles and replays on life-like courts 
featuring multiple playing surfaces.

-Sequel to the worldwide arcade and Dreamcast hit, Virtua Tennis.